puzzles.name: The Main Mechanic
puzzles.description: Use the arrow keys (or just swipe on mobile!) to move the blue players onto the green goals

puzzles.name: Lava
puzzles.description: If any blue player touches red, the level restarts

puzzles.name: Simultaneous
puzzles.description: All players must be on a goal simultaneously to win

puzzles.name: Early Bird
puzzles.description: You can move through and over goals freely, even if not all players are there at once (it won't help or hurt you)

puzzles.name: Coins
puzzles.description: All yellow coins must be collected before the goals will let you win

puzzles.name: Boulders
puzzles.description: If a player walks into a grey boulder, they stay still, and the boulder breaks

puzzles.name: Orange
puzzles.description: Orange squares turn red when the player stand on them: linger on the square at your peril!

puzzles.name: Merge
puzzles.description: If two players occupy the same square, they merge into one!
